data.description: Welcome to your move-in ready, updated 3-bed, 2-bath, 2-car garage home in Midway ISD! This sparkling gem boasts updated vinyl plank flooring & a host of upgrades. Enjoy cozy evenings in the spacious family room with a corner wood-burning fireplace & vaulted ceiling, open to the eating area & kitchen. Large picture windows overlook the backyard from the living & dining rooms, providing abundant natural light & a peaceful, cozy vibe. The updated kitchen features recently installed white cabinets, butcher block countertops, & white subway tile backsplash. The oversized primary suite awaits with a large walk-in closet & dual vanity. Outside, relax in the lush backyard oasis with a covered patio & privacy fence, perfect for entertaining. Located on a low-traffic street in the coveted Hillside neighborhood, this home offers easy access to Spring Valley Elementary, Hewitt Dr, Warren Park, & I-35. Don't miss out on this adorable home—schedule your showing today!
